::KitKat::

She transformed into bot mode and looked around.  Her sence f smell 
was stronger in beast mode, but in bot mode, it was still a strong 
sence. "Yeah, I smell it too.  I think that they went that way."  She 
shined the light down a long tunnel.
"Let's go." 
She walked down the tunnel and found it emptied into a larger cave 
with a pool in the middle of it.
"I can smell thier scent. It's really strong in this part of the 
cave."
She looked around but didn't see them. "I wonder where they went?"
Her instincts kicked in and she had a cold chill run up her back. She 
transformed back into wolf mode and looked about.  She saw large 
ripples in the pond and saw the foot prints in the dirt on the cave 
floor.
